SSN is a ninedigit number issued to US citizens permanent residents and temporary working residents under section 205c2 of the Social Security Act codified as 42 USC 405c2

Credit card number is the card identifier found on payment cards such as credit cards and debit cards The leading six digits of the card number is the issuer identification number The remaining numbers on the card except the last digit are the individual account identification number The last digit is the Luhn check digit https is enwikipediaorgwikiPaymentcardnumber
